narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: This course taught me to be more proficient in the Indonesian language and broadened my understanding of Indonesian culture more.
Learned lots about indonesia and the culture. Also discussed history and Indonesias colonialization.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The biggest strength of this course is the fun and engaging atmosphere. Also, this class pushes you the right amount to grow in your knowledge of the Indonesian language. I do not see any weaknesses in this course.
Loves how it was flexible to focus on what we were interested in.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, I would. This is a great class that you learn a lot in and don't receive too large of a workload in.
Yes definitely. It was so fun and flexible to what I was excited to learn about
